---
By: Chuang Tse
Locus:
  Page: 321
  Verse: 19
Tags:
  - Mind
---
The mind of the sage being in repose becomes the mirror of the universe.
The repose of the sage is not what the world calls repose. His repose is
the result of his mental attitude. All creation could not disturb his
equilibriumï¼š hence his repose.
